2. Run focused composition tests: `vitest run --config config/testing/vitest.config.ts src/tools/video-editor/runtime/composition/compositionGraphProjector.test.ts src/tools/video-editor/runtime/composition/patchPreview.test.ts src/tools/video-editor/runtime/composition/materialRuntime.test.ts`.
3. Run focused render tests: `vitest run --config config/testing/vitest.config.ts src/tools/video-editor/runtime/renderability.test.ts src/tools/video-editor/runtime/renderPlanner.test.ts src/tools/video-editor/runtime/renderPlanner.compositionGraph.test.ts src/tools/video-editor/runtime/extensionSurface.test.ts src/tools/video-editor/runtime/outputFormatRegistry.test.ts`.
4. Run `npm run lint` after the TypeScript surface settles.
5. Run `npm test` as the final broad gate.

